[3] Saudi Arabia, other theory on Taif outbreak
Date: Sat 25 Oct 2014
Source: Maktoob News, Saudi Gazette report [edited]
https://en-maktoob.news.yahoo.com/central-ac-linked-taif-mers-spread-081555689.html


Sources have revealed that they suspect the central air conditioning at the Taif Dialysis Center for spreading the Middle East respiratory syndrome coronavirus (MERS-CoV) in the center. The theory was put forward to explain how an employee in the IT department at the hospital tested positive for the virus.

Acting minister of health Adel Fakeih has visited the hospital and instructed the hospital's management to find suitable solutions and separate patient beds to prevent the virus from further spreading.

